tafsir[2]{c,v,t}:
  45,3,"Surely in the heavens and the earth are signs for the faithful. In this verse He shows to the creatures the perfection of His power in creating heaven and earth."
  45,4,"And in your creation and the beasts He has scattered are signs for a people who have certainty. He is making manifest His gentleness toward all animals and especially the Adamites."